The Mesen2 adapter's runtime Lua (emucap-core.lua plus the per-system entry
scripts emucap-snes.lua / emucap-sms.lua) is loaded at runtime by Mesen2 via a
command-line argument, not compiled or linked into the Mesen2 binary. It is
licensed GPL-2.0-or-later, the project default. Mesen2 itself is GPL-3.0-or-later;
see ../../NOTICE.

